{"word":"G2734 - κατοπτρίζομαι - katoptrízomai - kat-op-trid'-zom-ahee - Behold as in a glass","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατοπτρίζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>katoptrízomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kat-op-trid'-zom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Behold as in a glass"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கண்ணாடியிலே காண்கிறதுபோலக் காண்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to show in a mirror, to make to reflect, to mirror to look at oneself in a mirror"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Middle voice from a compound of <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3700 - ὀπτάνομαι - optánomai - op-tan'-om-ahee/3700\">G3700</a> (compare <a href=\"#/G2072 - ἔσοπτρον - ésoptron - es'-op-tron/2072\">G2072</a>); to <i>mirror oneself</i>, that is, to <i>see reflected</i> (figuratively): - behold as in a glass."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2072 - ἔσοπτρον - ésoptron - es'-op-tron/2072\">G2072</a>, <a href=\"#/G2734 - κατοπτρίζομαι - katoptrízomai - kat-op-trid'-zom-ahee/2734\">G2734</a>"}]}